            </h3>
            <p>
                Here are some of my recent blog posts and random ramblings.
                See also the full <a href="blog">blog posts</a> archive and
                below if you want to learn more about some of our
                <a href="#projects">projects</a>. You may also find more on
                <a href="https://twitter.com/another_clue">Twitter</a>.
            </p>
{% for post in data.posts[:3] %}
            <article>
                <h4><a href="{{ post.external_url | default("." ~ (post.url | replace({'.html':''}))) }}">{{ post.title }}</a></h4>
                <ul>
                    <li><time>{{ post.date | date("Y-m-d") }}</time></li>
{%     for tag in post.tags %}
                    <li><a href="blog#{{ tag }}" title="Show all blog posts tagged #{{ tag }} ({{ data.posts_tags[tag]|length }})" rel="tag">#{{ tag }}</a></li>
{%     endfor %}
                </ul>
                <p>{{ post.blocks.content|raw|striptags|replace({"\n":' ', "\r":' '})|trim|split(' ')|slice(0,50)|join(' ')|raw }}…</p>
                <a href="{{ post.external_url | default("." ~ (post.url | replace({'.html':''}))) }}"><em>Read more</em></a>
            </article>
{% endfor %}
            <p>
                <em>For more blog posts, see also the full <a href="blog">blog posts</a> archive.</em>
            </p>
